# A concise description of what this element means (e.g. for use in autogenerated summaries).
#: StructureDefinition.element.Medication.extension:classification/short
msgid "Klassifisering av legemidlet ved bruk av ATC-kode fra WHO ATC kodesystem."
msgstr "Classification of the medication using an ATC code from the WHO ATC code system."

# Provides a complete explanation of the meaning of the data element for human readability.  For the case of elements derived from existing elements (e.g. constraints), the definition SHALL be consistent with the base definition, but convey the meaning of the element in the particular context of use of the resource. (Note: The text you are reading is specified in ElementDefinition.definition).
#: StructureDefinition.element.Medication.extension:classification/definition
msgid "Klassifisering av legemidlet ved bruk av ATC-kode fra WHO ATC kodesystem. Et legemiddel har i utgangspunktet kun én ATC-kode."
msgstr "Classification of the medication using an ATC code from the WHO ATC code system. A medication normally has only one ATC code."

# Explanatory notes and implementation guidance about the data element, including notes about how to use the data properly, exceptions to proper use, etc. (Note: The text you are reading is specified in ElementDefinition.comment).
#: StructureDefinition.element.Medication.extension:classification/comment
msgid "Denne extension brukes for å angi legemidlets klassifisering i henhold til standardiserte kodesystemer, primært ATC-koder fra WHO."
msgstr "This extension is used to specify the medication's classification according to standardized code systems, primarily WHO ATC codes."

# A concise description of what this element means (e.g. for use in autogenerated summaries).
#: StructureDefinition.element.Medication.code/short
msgid "Identifikator fra FEST, SNOMED CT eller LokalLegemiddelkatalog. Hvis ikke fylt ut, skal ingredient ha verdi. Hvis LokaltLegemiddel er fylt ut bør ingredient ha verdi."
msgstr "Identifier from FEST, SNOMED CT, or the local medication catalog. If not populated, ingredient shall have a value. If LokaltLegemiddel is populated, ingredient should have a value."

