#: StructureDefinition.element.Medication.ingredient/short
msgid "Virkestoff(er) som inngår i legemiddelet. Skal fylles ut hvis code ikke har verdi. Bør fylles ut hvis code.coding[LokaltLegemiddel] har verdi."
msgstr "Ingredient(s) in the medication. Shall be populated if code has no value. Should be populated if code.coding[LokaltLegemiddel] has a value."

# Provides a complete explanation of the meaning of the data element for human readability.  For the case of elements derived from existing elements (e.g. constraints), the definition SHALL be consistent with the base definition, but convey the meaning of the element in the particular context of use of the resource. (Note: The text you are reading is specified in ElementDefinition.definition).
#: StructureDefinition.element.Medication.ingredient/definition
msgid "Virkestoff(er) som inngår i legemiddelet. Skal fylles ut hvis code ikke har verdi. Bør fylles ut hvis code.coding[LokaltLegemiddel] har verdi."
msgstr "Ingredient(s) in the medication. Shall be populated if code has no value. Should be populated if code.coding[LokaltLegemiddel] has a value."

# Explanatory notes and implementation guidance about the data element, including notes about how to use the data properly, exceptions to proper use, etc. (Note: The text you are reading is specified in ElementDefinition.comment).
#: StructureDefinition.element.Medication.ingredient/comment
msgid "For legemidler identifisert med FEST-koder (FestLegemiddeldose, FestLegemiddelMerkevare, FestLegemiddelpakning, FestLegemiddelVirkestoff, Varenummer) eller SNOMED CT er ingredient valgfritt, da virkestoffinformasjon kan hentes fra disse katalogene. For lokale legemidler anbefales det å oppgi ingredient for bedre sporbarhet."
msgstr "For medications identified with FEST codes (FestLegemiddeldose, FestLegemiddelMerkevare, FestLegemiddelpakning, FestLegemiddelVirkestoff, Varenummer) or SNOMED CT, ingredient is optional because substance information can be retrieved from those catalogs. For local medications, it is recommended to specify ingredient for better traceability."

